graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Component"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|manages| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Model Serving Components"
        Agent[Agent Sidecar<br/>Model lifecycle mgmt]
        Router[Router Sidecar<br/>InferenceGraph routing]
        StorageInit[Storage Initializer<br/>Init container]

        subgraph "Model Servers"
            SKLearn[sklearnserver<br/>Python REST/gRPC]
            XGB[xgbserver<br/>Python REST/gRPC]
            LGB[lgbserver<br/>Python REST/gRPC]
            Paddle[paddleserver<br/>Python REST/gRPC]
            PMML[pmmlserver<br/>Python REST/gRPC]
        end

        subgraph "Explainers"
            Alibi[alibiexplainer<br/>Model interpretability]
            ART[artexplainer<br/>Adversarial robustness]
            AIFair[aiffairness<br/>Bias detection]
        end
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InfSvc[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        ServRuntime[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InfGraph[InferenceGraph CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModel[TrainedModel CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|kubectl create| InfSvc
    InfSvc -->|watched by| Controller
    ServRuntime -->|watched by| Controller
    InfGraph -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModel -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService[Knative Service]
    Controller -->|creates| K8sDeploy[Kubernetes Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService]

    K8sDeploy -->|contains| Agent
    K8sDeploy -->|contains| Router
    K8sDeploy -->|init| StorageInit
    K8sDeploy -->|contains| SKLearn
    K8sDeploy -->|contains| XGB

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>v0.39.3]
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>v1.x]
        CertMgr[cert-manager<br/>v1.x]
    end

    Controller -->|depends on| Knative
    Controller -->|depends on| Istio
    Webhook -->|TLS certs| CertMgr

    subgraph "Storage Backends"
        S3[AWS S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    StorageInit -->|downloads models| S3
    StorageInit -->|downloads models| GCS
    StorageInit -->|downloads models| Azure

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integration"
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Storage URI]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>VirtualServices]
    end

    Controller -->|queries metadata| ModelRegistry
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceMesh

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style InfSvc fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style CertMgr fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style GCS fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Azure fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
